    title: 'Salesforce vs. HubSpot: How to Choose — and Actually Implement — the Right CRM',
    excerpt: `An operator's take on the Salesforce vs. HubSpot decision, why most CRM rollouts disappoint, and how to implement a system your sales team will actually use.`,
    category: 'Revenue Operations',
    date: 'May 9, 2026',
    lastUpdated: 'May 9, 2026',
